==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Ditokous
<hw>Di"to*kous</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[Gr. <grk>di-</grk>
= <grk>di`s-</grk> twice + <?/ a bringing forth, offspring.]</ety>
<fld>(Zool.)</fld> <sd>(a)</sd> <def>Having two kinds of young, as
certain annelids.</def> <sd>(b)</sd> <def>Producing only two eggs for a
clutch, as certain birds do.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Ditolyl</ent>⟦br⟧
